<div id="et-main-area">
	
<div id="main-content">


			
				<article id="post-301071" class="post-301071 page type-page status-publish hentry">

				
					<div class="entry-content">
					<div class="et-l et-l--post">
			<div class="et_builder_inner_content et_pb_gutters2">
		<div class="et_pb_section et_pb_section_0 et_pb_with_background et_section_regular section_has_divider et_pb_bottom_divider" >
				
				
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_row et_pb_row_0">
				<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4 et_pb_column_0  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child">
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_0  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_text_align_center-phone et_pb_bg_layout_light">
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner"><p><strong>Empowering Healthcare Professionals to Transform Postpartum Care</strong></p>
<p>Moms Deserve More Than a Six-Week Checkup</p></div>
			</div><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_1  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_text_align_center-phone et_pb_bg_layout_light">
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner"><p>Learn how to provide evidence-based postpartum care that supports mothers, babies, and families—enhancing recovery, bonding, and long-term wellbeing</p></div>
			</div><div class="et_pb_button_module_wrapper et_pb_button_0_wrapper et_pb_button_alignment_phone_center et_pb_module  dbdb-icon-on-right dbdb-icon-on-hover dbdb-has-custom-padding">
				<a class="et_pb_button et_pb_button_0 et_pb_bg_layout_light" href="https://thepostpartumot.com/contact/">Let&#039;s Chat</a>
			</div>
			</div>
				
				
				
				
			</div>
				
				<div class="et_pb_bottom_inside_divider et-no-transition"></div>
			</div><div class="et_pb_section et_pb_section_1 et_pb_with_background et_section_regular" >
				
				
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_row et_pb_row_1 et_pb_equal_columns">
				<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_3_5 et_pb_column_1  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough">
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_module et_pb_heading et_pb_heading_0 et_pb_bg_layout_">
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_heading_container"><h2 class="et_pb_module_heading">Revolutionizing Postpartum Care—One Mom, One Baby, and One Family at a Time</h2></div>
			</div><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_2  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_text_align_center-tablet et_pb_bg_layout_light">
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner"><p>Founded by Melissa O’Neal, OTR/L, The Postpartum OT equips healthcare professionals with the expertise to guide new mothers toward balance, confidence, and holistic wellness. Drawing on over a decade of practical experience, our mission is to help you serve postpartum families with evidence-based strategies—addressing physical recovery, emotional well-being, and the challenges of everyday life. Whether it’s teaching them how to navigate daily tasks, relieve discomfort, or rediscover a sense of “normal,” we’re here to provide the knowledge, tools, and unwavering support you need to make a transformative impact. </p></div>
			</div><div class="et_pb_button_module_wrapper et_pb_button_1_wrapper et_pb_button_alignment_tablet_center et_pb_button_alignment_phone_center et_pb_module  dbdb-icon-on-right dbdb-icon-on-hover dbdb-has-custom-padding">
				<a class="et_pb_button et_pb_button_1 et_pb_bg_layout_light" href="https://calendar.app.google/s3btABbwoVQjR17v9" target="_blank">Let&#039;s Chat</a>
			</div>
			</div><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_2_5 et_pb_column_2  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child">
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_module et_pb_image et_pb_image_0">
				
				
				
				
				<span class="et_pb_image_wrap "><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="1920" height="2560" src="https://thepostpartumot.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/IMG_1812.jpg" alt="" title="The Postpartum OT" srcset="https://thepostpartumot.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/IMG_1812.jpg 1920w, https://thepostpartumot.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/IMG_1812-1280x1707.jpg 1280w, https://thepostpartumot.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/IMG_1812-980x1307.jpg 980w, https://thepostpartumot.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/IMG_1812-480x640.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) and (max-width: 980px) 980px, (min-width: 981px) and (max-width: 1280px) 1280px, (min-width: 1281px) 1920px, 100vw" class="wp-image-301898" /></span>
			</div>
			</div>
				
				
				
				
			</div>
				
				
			</div><div class="et_pb_with_border et_pb_section et_pb_section_2 et_section_regular" >
				
				
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_row et_pb_row_3">
				<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_3 et_pb_column_3  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough">
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_module et_pb_image et_pb_image_1">
				
				
				
				
				<span class="et_pb_image_wrap "><img decoding="async" width="1920" height="2560" src="https://thepostpartumot.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/IMG_8865.jpg" alt="" title="IMG_8865" srcset="https://thepostpartumot.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/IMG_8865.jpg 1920w, https://thepostpartumot.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/IMG_8865-1280x1707.jpg 1280w, https://thepostpartumot.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/IMG_8865-980x1307.jpg 980w, https://thepostpartumot.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/IMG_8865-480x640.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) and (max-width: 980px) 980px, (min-width: 981px) and (max-width: 1280px) 1280px, (min-width: 1281px) 1920px, 100vw" class="wp-image-301901" /></span>
			</div>
			</div><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_2_3 et_pb_column_4  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child">
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_module et_pb_heading et_pb_heading_1 et_pb_bg_layout_">
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_heading_container"><h2 class="et_pb_module_heading">Key Benefits of Working Together</h2></div>
			</div><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_heading et_pb_heading_2 et_pb_bg_layout_">
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_heading_container"><h3 class="et_pb_module_heading">01. Leverage Over a Decade of Specialized Experience</h3></div>
			</div><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_3  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light">
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner"><p>Drawing on 10+ years of hands-on work in postpartum care, I’ll share real-world insights to help you confidently launch and grow your own postpartum practice. From day one, you’ll benefit from my hard-earned lessons, occupational therapy expertise, and extensive continuing education—giving you a head start on the path to success.</p></div>
			</div><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_heading et_pb_heading_3 et_pb_bg_layout_">
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_heading_container"><h3 class="et_pb_module_heading">02. Get Comprehensive Support Across All Areas of Postpartum Care</h3></div>
			</div><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_4  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light">
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner"><p>Postpartum involves so much more than just physical recovery. Together, we’ll dive into mental health, infant sleep, feeding, development, roles and routines, environment setup, and beyond. My holistic approach equips you with the knowledge to address every corner of your clients’ postpartum journey.</p></div>
			</div><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_heading et_pb_heading_4 et_pb_bg_layout_">
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_heading_container"><h3 class="et_pb_module_heading">03. Streamline Your Launch and Avoid Overwhelm</h3></div>
			</div><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_5  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light">
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner"><p>Building a postpartum practice can feel daunting without the right guidance. I’m here to ease that burden by providing clear, step-by-step strategies, proven resources, and time-saving tools. You’ll have a roadmap designed to help you focus on what matters most—caring for new moms and their families.</p></div>
			</div><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_heading et_pb_heading_5 et_pb_bg_layout_">
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_heading_container"><h3 class="et_pb_module_heading">04. Gain Ongoing Mentorship, Resources, and Confidence</h3></div>
			</div><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_6  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light">
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner"><p>You’re never alone in this journey. Beyond our initial work together, you’ll have continued access to support, updated resources, and a community ready to help you succeed. Feel empowered knowing you have a trusted mentor and a reliable network in your corner, every step of the way.</p></div>
			</div>
			</div>
				
				
				
				
			</div>
				
				
			</div><div class="et_pb_section et_pb_section_3 et_pb_with_background et_section_regular" >
				
				
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_row et_pb_row_4">
				<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4 et_pb_column_5  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child">
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_module et_pb_heading et_pb_heading_6 et_pb_bg_layout_">
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_heading_container"><h3 class="et_pb_module_heading">The postpartum period shapes not just the health of a mother, but the foundation of an entire family. When we support families during these critical first weeks, we're not just helping them survive—we're empowering them to thrive. This ripple effect touches everything: maternal mental health, infant development, family bonding, and the long-term wellbeing of our communities. Every family deserves this level of care, yet it's often the most overlooked phase of the parenting journey.</h3></div>
			</div>
			</div>
				
				
				
				
			</div>
				
				
			</div><div class="et_pb_section et_pb_section_4 et_pb_with_background et_section_regular" >
				
				
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_row et_pb_row_5 et_pb_equal_columns">
				<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_2 et_pb_column_6  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough">
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_module et_pb_heading et_pb_heading_7 et_pb_bg_layout_">
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_heading_container"><h2 class="et_pb_module_heading">Get Started – Schedule a Free 15-Minute Consultation</h2></div>
			</div><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_7  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_text_align_center-tablet et_pb_bg_layout_light">
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner"><p>Ready to tap into over 10 years of specialized postpartum experience? Take the first step toward feeling more confident in launching or expanding your own postpartum practice. During this quick call, we’ll discuss your goals, address any challenges, and explore how The Postpartum OT can guide you toward success. There’s no pressure—just a safe, open space to plan your next best step in helping new families thrive.</p></div>
			</div><div class="et_pb_button_module_wrapper et_pb_button_2_wrapper et_pb_button_alignment_tablet_center et_pb_button_alignment_phone_center et_pb_module  dbdb-icon-on-right dbdb-icon-on-hover dbdb-has-custom-padding">
				<a class="et_pb_button et_pb_button_2 et_pb_bg_layout_light" href="https://calendar.app.google/s3btABbwoVQjR17v9" target="_blank">Schedule a Call</a>
			</div><div class="et_pb_button_module_wrapper et_pb_button_3_wrapper et_pb_button_alignment_tablet_center et_pb_button_alignment_phone_center et_pb_module  dbdb-icon-on-right dbdb-icon-on-hover dbdb-has-custom-padding">
				<a class="et_pb_button et_pb_button_3 et_pb_bg_layout_light" href="https://www.facebook.com/share/g/1DgoR8tPMB/?mibextid=wwXIfr" target="_blank">Join Facebook Group</a>
			</div>
			</div><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_2 et_pb_column_7  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child">
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_module et_pb_image et_pb_image_2">
				
				
				
				
				<span class="et_pb_image_wrap "><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="750" src="https://thepostpartumot.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Midwifery.jpg" alt="" title="Midwifery" srcset="https://thepostpartumot.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Midwifery.jpg 1200w, https://thepostpartumot.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Midwifery-980x613.jpg 980w, https://thepostpartumot.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Midwifery-480x300.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) and (max-width: 980px) 980px, (min-width: 981px) 1200px, 100vw" class="wp-image-302045" /></span>
			</div>
			</div>
				
				
				
				
			</div>
				
				
			</div>		</div>
	</div>
						</div>

				
				</article>

			

</div>

